title: November Unemployment Rate in Michigan Counties
name: November Unemployment Rate in Michigan Counties
description: The map is based on county level unemployment rates for November, 2007 in Michigan. Source: http://www.milmi.org/?PAGEID=67&SUBID=200Michigan is probably the only state that has lost jobs over the last six years. The job-loss has become one of the major issues in 2008 Republican Election primaries and all major contenders in the Republican primary have been using that issue to canvass for the votes. Democratic party has no candidates on the primary ballot except Clinton, because the result of National Democratic Party stripping Michigan of all its delegates in response to Michigan moving its primary to earlier date.
